---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ImageOverview from '/public/qa-course/overview-image.svg';
---

<section id='qaoverview' class='container max-w-screen-desktop'>
  <header class='mb-3 grid gap-y-3'>
    <p class='text-xxs text-gray-700'>OVERVIEW</p>
    <h1 class='text-l font-bold tracking-widest text-black'>Learn by doing</h1>
  </header>
  <p class='text-s text-gray-700'>
    Through our bootcamp, you'll actively participate in coding exercises,
    project-based assignments, and simulated real-world scenarios. This hands-on
    approach not only solidifies your understanding but also cultivates
    problem-solving abilities, critical thinking, and confidence in applying
    learned concepts to your future jobs.
  </p>

  <figure class='mt-4'>
    <Image
      src={ImageOverview}
      alt='overview-image'
      loading='lazy'
      decoding='async'
      class='w-full'
    />
  </figure>
</section>
